        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "and what the world offered and especially his culture and family",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 115,
          "y_px": 44
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "His working life included maritime industries of Pearling and Crayfishing",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 89,
          "y_px": 61
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "He joined his Ancestors at age 80yrs. ",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 183,
          "y_px": 169
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": ". An avid musician and member of many bands he continued to various play instruments into his old age",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 15,
          "y_px": 141
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "In later life, he committed to serving the Lord and in 1999 was ordained an Anglican priest",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 48,
          "y_px": 156
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "A passionate sportsman and trainer in Boxing and Karate",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 126,
          "y_px": 110
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "as was a member of the landmark 1968 World Record tracklaying in the Pilbara.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 77,
          "y_px": 92
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "He spent brief time cutting Sugarcane before heading to Western Australia",
        "font": {
          "family": "Lucida Calligraphy",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 86,
          "y_px": 77
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#c99d44",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
